{"tid":201793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[收工]美軍官:除非北韓導彈瞄準美日韓,否則不會武力回應~","createTime":"2017-04-15T04:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T08:34:48.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"559a78e40e0b6d20b08fa42c0947c57e2ee0227b","tid":201793,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/503091/即時新聞/人民軍指或以核武回應美軍事挑釁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F503091%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E8%BB%8D%E6%8C%87%E6%88%96%E4%BB%A5%E6%A0%B8%E6%AD%A6%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=89164631\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F503091%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E8%BB%8D%E6%8C%87%E6%88%96%E4%BB%A5%E6%A0%B8%E6%AD%A6%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81&h=3f8c5cd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/503091/即時新聞/人民軍指或以核武回應美軍事挑釁</a><br />\n<br />\n人民軍指或以核武回應美軍事挑釁<br />\n<br />\n2017/04/15 07:00<br />\n<br />\n今天是北韓太陽節，外界估計當局最快或今天第六次核試，北韓人民軍總參謀部批評，朝鮮半島當前局勢是美國總統特朗普過度軍事挑釁造成，不排除以核武回應。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n因應北韓近月多次試射彈道導彈，美軍日前調派核動力航母卡爾文森號戰鬥群，到朝鮮半島一帶提升警戒。北韓人民軍總參謀部周五發聲明，批評特朗普政府對平壤的軍事挑釁，已達不容忽視的程度，朝鮮半島局勢嚴峻也是對方造成。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n聲明提及人民軍會以超強硬方式，粉碎美國挑釁，視乎美國挑釁的方式和程度。以核打擊在內的選項回應，揚言只需數分鐘，便能摧毀美軍駐南韓基地、青瓦台，亦有能力攻擊日本，甚至美國本土目標。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周四飛抵佛羅里達與妻子及家人度周末，白宮透露，國家安全委員會成員亦有隨行，一旦北韓有所動作，總統會即時獲知會。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社引述官員消息，特朗普政府經過兩個月檢討定出對朝政策，得出的結論是須借助中國的影響力，向北韓作最大程度施壓，同時不放棄與平壤建立關係。該名官員強調，華府目前沒與北韓有任何聯繫，任何接觸均須以平壤無核化為大前提。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報道同時引述美軍官員稱，除非北韓把導彈瞄準美、日、韓任何一國，否則無意以武力回應平壤核試或試射導彈。&nbsp;</span><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外長王毅周五與俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫通電話時表示，防止朝鮮半島生戰生亂，符合中俄共同利益，中方願同俄方合作，推動有關各方恢復對話，令局勢降溫。"},{"pid":"ed9da8cb7ead088d6d8f0669d2ad555bdff9c1f4","tid":201793,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"又話核試就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbe60ffed9f37574a418c73ae788d1fd3f01102","tid":201793,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339f5d92e428c1abf595b7421da39327224e39fa","tid":201793,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"913e21e71a25ae5bb87f7a51af2febc618b6f185","tid":201793,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話核試就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇香港傳媒吹?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1417253c7c276d692824e96ac95ed2a2caee2ac0","tid":201793,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4512a3ef5e15285c65617cb25af44480612e0265","tid":201793,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5260180512bdf891a20cc348b25073b8a39fece5","tid":201793,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:57:19.000Z","msg":"屌 世界警察笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25094382e9dd720e46b385f5b22465242618080","tid":201793,"uid":42090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:58:02.000Z","msg":"好波，peaceful<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820de9a4e02cd0c62774f8c8f486050fc6fcc51d","tid":201793,"uid